<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard - Make a Difference</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: url('/images/donation\ page.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Dark overlay for better text visibility */
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .quote {
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #FFD700;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #FFD700; /* Gold button */
            color: #333;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #FFBF00;
        }

        footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="overlay"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Your Dashboard</h1>
        <div class="quote">"Act as if what you do makes a difference. It does." – William James</div>
        <p>Thank you for being a part of this mission to make the world a better place. Your efforts and contributions matter.</p>
        <form action="/auth/dashboard/checkout" method="POST">
        <button type="submit">Donate Now</button>
    </form>
    </div>
    <a href="/auth/logout">Logout</a>
    <footer>
        <p>© 2024 Make a Difference. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
